{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/playcanvas/awesome-playcanvas/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b9a69c72-9f8b-5658-af30-1d339be09eb9","html":"<h1 id=\"awesome-playcanvas-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-playcanvas-awesome\" aria-label=\"awesome playcanvas awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome PlayCanvas <a href=\"https://awesome.re\"><img src=\"https://awesome.re/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<img src=\"https://github.com/playcanvas/awesome-playcanvas/raw/master/playcanvas-logo.png\" align=\"right\" width=\"100\">\n<p><a href=\"https://playcanvas.com/\">PlayCanvas</a> is an open source platform for building interactive web content. It's written in JavaScript, HTML5, CSS3 and WebGL.</p>\n<p>This list is a curated collection of awesome resources, tools, tutorials and projects using the PlayCanvas engine to help developers make <em>awesome</em> games and visualizations.</p>\n<p>Contributions <em>very welcome</em> but first see <a href=\"#contributing\">Contributing</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#playcanvas\">PlayCanvas</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#community\">Community</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#tutorials\">Tutorials</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#extensions-and-utilities\">Extensions and Utilities</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#technical-demos\">Technical Demos</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#advertising\">Advertising</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#browser-games\">Browser Games</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#io-games\">IO Games</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#messenger-games\">Messenger Games</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#automotive\">Automotive</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#product-configurators\">Product Configurators</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#arvrxr\">AR/VR/XR</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#blockchaincryptonft\">Blockchain/Crypto/NFT</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#virtual-events\">Virtual Events</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"playcanvas\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#playcanvas\" aria-label=\"playcanvas permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>PlayCanvas</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://playcanvas.com/\">Editor</a> - Browser-based, real-time collaborative WebGL Editor.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/playcanvas/engine\">Engine</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/playcanvas/engine\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">6.3k</span></span></a> - Full source to the PlayCanvas run-time licensed under MIT.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://playcanvas.com/viewer\">glTF Viewer</a> - glTF 2.0 compliant model viewer.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/playcanvas\">NPM Package</a> - Node.js packages of the PlayCanvas engine run-time.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://playcanvas.github.io/pcui/\">PCUI</a> - Open source front-end framework used by the PlayCanvas toolset.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.playcanvas.com/en/api/\">Reference</a> - API reference manual for the engine run-time.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.playcanvas.com/en/user-manual/\">User Manual</a> - PlayCanvas user guide.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"community\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#community\" aria-label=\"community permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Community</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://forum.playcanvas.com/\">Forum</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/playcanvas\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://discord.gg/RSaMRzg\">Discord Server</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/playcanvas/\">Facebook</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.html5gamedevs.com/tags/playcanvas/\">HTML5GameDevs Forum</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://openbase.com/js/playcanvas\">Openbase</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/PlayCanvas/\">Reddit</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/playcanvas\">Stack Overflow</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"tutorials\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tutorials\" aria-label=\"tutorials permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tutorials</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.gamefromscratch.com/post/2017/05/25/PlayCanvas-Engine-Revisited.aspx\">Create a Bowling Game</a> - Create a physics-based bowling game.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gamedevelopment.tutsplus.com/tutorials/create-a-space-shooter-with-playcanvas-part-1--cms-28066\">Create a Space Shooter</a> - Recreate Asteroids in this Tutsplus tutorial.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.codemahal.com/tutorials/playcanvas/\">Game Design with PlayCanvas and JavaScript</a> - PlayCanvas training series.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Games/Techniques/3D_on_the_web/Building_up_a_basic_demo_with_PlayCanvas\">MDN tutorial</a> - Build up a basic demo with PlayCanvas.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.playcanvas.com/en/tutorials/\">Official Tutorials</a> - Large collection of official PlayCanvas tutorials.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://magazine.substance3d.com/high-end-renders-online-bike-configurator-substance/\">PlayCanvas and Substance</a> - Creating high-end artwork for vehicle configurators with PlayCanvas and Substance.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://pirron.one/playingincanvas/\">Playing in Canvas</a> - Pirron One's PlayCanvas themed blog.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/@omar4ur/rescue-the-lunar-lander-a-coderdojo-tutorial-5217d463e26a\">Rescue the Lunar Lander</a> - Tutorial to make a simple physics based game.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLy57qL2R3Z6NlBQBEMnjVPT0iz320i4Ko\">Video Tutorials</a> - YouTube playlist for short PlayCanvas tutorials.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"extensions-and-utilities\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#extensions-and-utilities\" aria-label=\"extensions and utilities permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Extensions and Utilities</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.8thwall.com/docs/web/#getting-started-with-playcanvas\">8th Wall</a> - Markerless AR runtime.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/playcanvas/playcanvas-ar\">playcanvas-ar</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/playcanvas/playcanvas-ar\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">175</span></span></a> - Marker-based AR solution built on ARTollkit.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/yushimatenjin/playcanvas-node\">playcanvas-node</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/yushimatenjin/playcanvas-node\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4</span></span></a> - REST API wrapper for Node.js.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/playcanvas/playcanvas-p2.js\">playcanvas-p2.js</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/playcanvas/playcanvas-p2.js\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">17</span></span></a> - An integration with the p2.js 2D physics engine.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/playcanvas/playcanvas-spine\">playcanvas-spine</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/playcanvas/playcanvas-spine\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">33</span></span></a> - Spine plugin for PlayCanvas for 2D animations.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/playcanvas/playcanvas-tween\">playcanvas-tween</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/playcanvas/playcanvas-tween\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">32</span></span></a> - Officially supported tween animation plugin.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/isobolewski/playcanvas-vue\">playcanvas-vue</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/isobolewski/playcanvas-vue\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">19</span></span></a> - A PlayCanvas integration with Vue.js.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/tweenjs/tween.js/\">tween.js</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/tweenjs/tween.js/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">8k</span></span></a> - Popular JavaScript tweening library that integrates easily with PlayCanvas.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pic.pirron-rodon.one\">Pirron One</a> - Editor externsions implementing post effects, terrain creation and more.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/playcanvas/sublime-completions\">Sublime Completions</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/playcanvas/sublime-completions\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">3</span></span></a> - Sublime Text Autocompletion for the PlayCanvas API.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"technical-demos\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#technical-demos\" aria-label=\"technical demos permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Technical Demos</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://playcanv.as/p/44MRmJRU/\">After the Flood</a> - Collaboration with Mozilla to promote WebGL 2.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://playcanv.as/p/LpmXGUe6/\">Casino</a> - Physically rendered 3D casino environment.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://playcanv.as/p/ZV4PW6wr/\">Global Illumination</a> - GI approximation using interpolated lightmaps.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://playcanv.as/p/MflWvdTW/\">Seemore</a> - Collaboration with ARM to promote mobile WebGL.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://playcanv.as/p/txPePQvy/\">Sponza</a> - Run-time lightmapped Sponza environment.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://playcanv.as/p/SA7hVBLt/\">Star-Lord</a> - First ever PBR demo from PlayCanvas.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://playcanv.as/p/nL1dYbMv\">Steampunk Slots</a> - Physically rendered slots machine.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"advertising\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#advertising\" aria-label=\"advertising permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Advertising</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://zx-game.de\">Adidas ZX Game</a> - Branded rhythm action game (German).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.allyracer.com/\">Ally Racing</a> - Retro NASCAR racing adver-game for Ally Bank.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://gun.playcanvas.com/\">Call of Duty: Gunsmith</a> - Promotional 3D experience themed on Call of Duty.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vz777.com/cybercity/index.html\">Cyber City</a> - Promotional site for Visionaries777.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vimeo.com/136313614\">DOOH Invaders</a> - World's largest Space Invaders clone unveiled at Cannes Lions.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.ebay-report.de/\">eBay Report</a> - Stats and facts from eBay Germany.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://playcanv.as/p/A5qC9ftM/?overlay=false\">Fatal System Error</a> - Interactive opera experience created by Dumbworld from the Royal Opera House.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://mmx.playcanvas.com/?truck=johncena\">MMX Racing</a> - Interactive 3D ad for a popular mobile game.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vimeo.com/152996271\">Ride Along 2</a> - Using WebGL to promote a Hollywood movie release.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=onOJBCC8R7A\">Rugby World Cup</a> - Promoting the Rugby World Cup in London's Piccadilly Circus.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"browser-games\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#browser-games\" aria-label=\"browser games permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Browser Games</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/cbbc/games/beyond-bionic-extreme-encounters\">Beyond Bionic: Extreme Encounters</a> - Outdoor adventures in this game from the BBC.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://partners.disney.com/hour-of-code\">Disney's Hour of Code - Moana</a> - Learn programming fundamentals with Disney's Moana.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://playcanv.as/p/2OlkUaxF/\">Flappy Bird</a> - Guide the bird through as many pipes as possible.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://playcanv.as/p/Ikq6Uk6A/\">Galaxies: Combat</a> - Carefully select power ups to defeat waves of hostile ships.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.gamee.com/game/geometryrun\">Geometry Run</a> - Stylized endless runner built from geometric shapes.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.toggo.de/spiele/jurassic-world/jurassic-world-das-gelaenderennen-6727.htm\">Lego Jurassic World: Off-road Race</a> - Dinosaurs, LEGO and vehicle stunts.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://playmegopoly.com/\">Megopoly</a> - Free to play casual strategy board game where you invest in virtual property.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://benbean.tech/monopoly-io/\">Monopoly</a> - The classic boardgame recreated in a 3D video game.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gamedistribution.com/games/nitro-knights\">Nitro Knights</a> - Futuristic jousting game.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://playcanv.as/p/3G3RnfUz/\">Orbital Survival</a> - Destroy wave after wave of enemies on a tiny world.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.starstable.com/en/register\">Star Stable</a> - Character registration portal for popular horse game.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://poki.com/en/g/stickman-climb\">Stickman Climb</a> - Physics based puzzle game.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://playcanv.as/p/JtL2iqIH/\">SWOOOP</a> - Pick up gems in a bi-plane above a magical island.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gala.games\">Town Star</a> - Online farming game built by the Creative Director of Farmville 2.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.miniclip.com/games/virtual-voodoo/en/\">Virtual Voodoo</a> - Voodoo doll simulator.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"io-games\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#io-games\" aria-label=\"io games permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>IO Games</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.bulletbonanza.io/\">Bullet Bonanza</a> - Fast paced, high fidelity, 3D Multiplayer FPS game from Kiloo.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://inkwars.io/\">Ink Wars</a> - Real-time multiplayer game where you paint the neighborhood to win.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://miniroyale2.io/\">Mini Royale 2</a> - Battle Royale first person shooter.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://robostorm.io/\">Robostorm</a> - Frenetic online multiplayer mech battle game.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://tankroyale.io/\">Tank Royale</a> - Cartoony fast-paced top-down multiplayer shooter.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://tanx.io\">TANX</a> - Online multiplayer tank battle game.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://poki.com/en/g/venge-io\">Venge</a> - 3D Multiplayer FPS shooter.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"messenger-games\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#messenger-games\" aria-label=\"messenger games permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Messenger Games</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://support.snapchat.com/en-GB/a/games\">Snap Games Support</a> - Snapchat's gaming platform powered by PlayCanvas.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/instantgames/play/2236502786367605/\">Archery 3D</a> - Archery simulator.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/gamebytes-games-for-imessage/id1506797690\">GameBytes</a> - Multiplayer games for iMessage.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/instantgames/play/267920816949420/\">Golden Boot</a> - Penalty kick game.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/instantgames/play/188237332468920/\">Hoop Master</a> - Head to head basketball game.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/instantgames/play/1315812941823883/\">Master Archer</a> - Shoot the fruit from the top of Bob's head.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/instantgames/play/351725822100289/\">Let's Craft</a> - Sandbox voxel-building game.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"automotive\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#automotive\" aria-label=\"automotive permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Automotive</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.airstream.com/travel-trailers/airstream-basecamp-3d-experience/\">Airstream Basecamp</a> - Travel trailer visualizer.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.benningtonmarine.com/en-us/build-model/\">Bennington Pontoon Boats</a> - Boat configurator.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.bmw.com/en/design/car-design-the-keys-to-bmw-design.html\">BMW Car Design</a> - Interactive exploration of BMW design.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://car.playcanvas.com\">BMW i8</a> - Car visualizer.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://dabmotors.com/configurator/\">DAB Motors</a> - Motorcycle configurator.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.indianmotorcycle.com/en-us/scout-bobber/build-color/\">Indian Motorcycles</a> - Motorcycle configurator.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://beijing.infiniti-experience.com/\">Infiniti Experience</a> - Explore the 2020 Infiniti range (Chinese).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.kiavirtualexperience.com/\">Kia Virtual Experience</a> - Explore Kia's latest line of cars.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://rzr.polaris.com/en-us/build-model/\">Polaris RZR</a> - Off-road vehicle configurator.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"product-configurators\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#product-configurators\" aria-label=\"product configurators permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Product Configurators</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://3dplans.com\">3D Plans</a> - Virtual tours and interactive maps for the property market.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.amisco.com/en_us/uprightstool\">Amisco Furniture</a> - Interactive 3D furniture configurator.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.aritcohomelifts.com/build-your-lift/\">Aritco Home Lifts</a> - Elevator configurator.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://elfa.com/sv-se/planner\">Elfa Closets</a> - Closet configurator.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.sesotec.com/na/en-US/lp/nexwey\">Sesotec Nexwey</a> - Checkweigher machine visualizer.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://phone.playcanvas.com\">iPhone 6</a> - iPhone visualizer.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.myslidingwardrobe.co.uk/design-your-wardrobe/\">My Sliding Wardrobe</a> - Closet configurator.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.renewalbyandersen.com/windows-doors/replacement-windows/double-hung\">Renewal by Andersen Windows</a> - Window configurator.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.vaxthusguiden.se/\">Willab Gardens Greenhouses</a> - Greenhouse configurator.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"arvrxr\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href